Title: How Does It Feel to Be a Heart?
Description: July 24
---
Once a young woman said to me, “How does it feel to be a man?”
And I replied, “My dear, I am not so sure.” Then she said,
 “Well, aren’t you a man?”
And this time I responded, “I view gender as a beautiful animal that
 people often take
for a walk on a leash and might enter into some odd contest ... in hopes
 of winning a strange prize.”
My dear, a better question for Hafiz would have been, “How does it feel
 to be a heart?”
For all I know is love, and I now find my heart infinite, and everywher
